b"3/ $FLO completed their acquisition of former Hostess bread brands including Wonder, Merita, Home Pride, and Butternut in Feb '13. Competitor $BMBOY shows that bread is the most profitable grocery category in a '19 presentation. https://t.co/cWTbjfwwlu"

b"2/ The direct-store-delivery (DSD) area for $FLO has increased substantially from '03 to '19. Singled out in the '13 annual report as the first bread brand in the U.S. to have annual retail sales of $1.1 Bn, Nature's Own is their all star brand. https://t.co/740Rjwjf49"

b"1/ $10,000 invested in Flowers Foods $FLO in Dec '72 turned into more than $17 Mn by '14 per the 100 Baggers book. The '19 annual report shows that they are #2 in U.S. Breads, Buns and Rolls behind Bimbo Bakeries USA (BBU) of Grupo Bimbo $BMBOY. https://t.co/h1GU26uVa6"
